---
const stats = [
  { value: 'Â£45bn', label: 'Lost Every Year', description: 'Mental health costs destroy UK business profits' },
  { value: '1 in 3', label: 'Employees Struggling', description: 'Post-pandemic mental health crisis deepens' },
  { value: '62%', label: 'Workforce Stressed', description: 'Highest workplace stress levels ever recorded' },
  { value: '12.8m', label: 'Days Lost Annually', description: 'Productivity vanishing to stress-related absence' }
];

const warningSignsData = [
  { icon: 'calendar', title: 'Chronic Absenteeism', description: 'Sick days spiraling out of control' },
  { icon: 'users', title: 'Staff Exodus', description: 'Top talent walking out the door' },
  { icon: 'trending-down', title: 'Productivity Collapse', description: 'Performance metrics in free fall' },
  { icon: 'alert-circle', title: 'Team Breakdown', description: 'Conflicts and grievances escalating' },
  { icon: 'frown', title: 'Morale Crisis', description: 'Engagement scores hitting rock bottom' },
  { icon: 'x-circle', title: 'Recruitment Nightmare', description: "Can't attract or retain quality hires" }
];
---

<section id="problem" class="section bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 via-white to-primary-50/20">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-gray-900 mb-4">The Hidden Cost of Poor Mental Health in the Workplace</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-4">
        UK businesses are facing a wellbeing crisis that's impacting bottom lines, productivity, 
        and talent retention. Without proper workplace culture assessment and employee satisfaction measurement, 
        organizations miss critical warning signs until it's too late.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Mental health in the workplace affects every metric that matters - from absenteeism and turnover 
        to innovation and customer satisfaction. Our workplace wellbeing assessments help identify these 
        issues before they become costly problems.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Statistics Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16">
      {stats.map((stat, index) => (
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1"
             style={`animation-delay: ${index * 0.1}s`}>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">{stat.value}</div>
          <div class="text-gray-900 font-semibold mb-1">{stat.label}</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">{stat.description}</div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Warning Signs Section -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <!-- Content Side -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Is Your Organisation Experiencing These Warning Signs?
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Mental health in the workplace has become the defining challenge for UK businesses. 
            Employee burnout statistics show that workplace stress costs British companies billions annually. 
            Poor workplace culture directly impacts employee satisfaction measurement scores, leading to a 
            cascade of problems: reduced productivity, higher turnover, and damaged employer brand.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            The pandemic fundamentally changed how we work, yet many organizations still rely on outdated 
            assessment methods. Traditional annual surveys fail to capture the nuanced reality of modern 
            workplace wellbeing. Without comprehensive workplace culture assessment, companies miss critical 
            insights about team dynamics, stress patterns, and engagement drivers.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Research shows that organizations conducting regular employee satisfaction measurement and workplace 
            wellbeing assessments are 3x more likely to retain top talent. They identify problems earlier, 
            implement targeted interventions, and create cultures where employees thrive.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            The good news? A professional workplace wellbeing audit provides the roadmap to transform these 
            challenges into competitive advantages, improving both employee satisfaction and business performance.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Warning Signs Grid -->
        <div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-50 to-orange-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Critical Warning Signs</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Is your organisation in crisis?</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            {warningSignsData.map((sign) => (
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors group">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:bg-red-200 transition-colors">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm mb-1">{sign.title}</h5>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">{sign.description}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-400 rounded-lg">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm">Experiencing 3+ Warning Signs?</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">
                  Your organisation needs immediate intervention. Our comprehensive wellbeing audit can 
                  identify root causes and provide actionable solutions before it's too late.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Don't let poor wellbeing continue to impact your organisation's success
      </p>
      <a href="#assessment" class="btn-primary">Get Your Free Wellbeing Assessment</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>